Class ValueHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vectorprint.report.data.types.ValueHelper

  • public class ValueHelper
extends Object
    provides convenience methods to create ReportValues as well as a method to get hold of a calendar that solves problems with week numbers.
    Author:
    Eduard Drenth at VectorPrint.nl
